[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0128","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0467","title":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Webcom CGI Guestbook 的 wguest.exe 和 rguest.exe 组件存在任意文件读取漏洞。攻击者可通过向 \"template\" 参数传入恶意路径，利用目录遍历技术读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响运行 Webcom Guestbook 0.1 版本的 Web 服务器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级至最新版本或移除存在漏洞的 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0467"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.433","remediation":"立即删除或禁用服务器上的 wguest.exe 和 rguest.exe 脚本，停止使用 Webcom CGI Guestbook 程序（已停止维护多年）。作为替代方案，部署其他仍在维护的留言本程序。同时配置 Web 服务器权限，限制 CGI 目录下脚本对任意文件的读取能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0467","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20446","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0467","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0467.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrcj-vcw6-vg5f/GHSA-rrcj-vcw6-vg5f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0467.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3c4e87d4-fd7c-4a07-bd95-3b0615781d90.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0128.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0128.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0133","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0469","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 窗口欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 存在窗口欺骗漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用浏览器窗口地址栏与内容区域显示不一致的缺陷，伪装成合法网站诱导用户访问。当用户浏览攻击者控制的页面时，浏览器地址栏可显示为受信任域名，而实际内容区域加载的是恶意页面，导致用户误信并输入敏感信息（如账号密码、信用卡号等），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上 Internet Explorer 5.0 及早期版本，攻击条件低，仅需用户点击恶意链接即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0469"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.857","remediation":"立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.01 SP2 中修复。对于仍使用 IE 的旧系统，建议禁用 Active Scripting 功能并启用 Internet 区域安全级别为「高」，同时考虑迁移至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0469","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0469","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0469.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3pmw-j7vc-7gww/GHSA-3pmw-j7vc-7gww.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82851/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000590.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--068ab4eb-23e0-450f-9ef2-37fd804f7644.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0133.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0153","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0480","title":"GNU Midnight Commander 符号链接攻击拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Midnight Commander 4.x 版本存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在当前目录下创建恶意符号链接，诱使 Midnight Commander 在处理文件列表时错误地跟随该链接，导致程序崩溃或资源耗尽，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Midnight Commander 4.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0480"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.260","remediation":"升级 Midnight Commander 至 4.5.50 及以上版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，可通过 `mc --no-subshell` 启动以降低攻击面，并避免在不可信目录中使用 MC 的文件管理功能。在系统层面，可将 `/tmp` 挂载为 `noexec`、`nodev`、`nosuid` 以限制本地攻击者的提权路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0480"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0168","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0443","title":"BMC Patrol 管理软件重放攻击漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol 管理软件存在认证会话重放漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络捕获并重放有效的管理员认证数据包，从而获取管理员密码并完全控制受影响的 Patrol 管理控制台。该漏洞源于会话令牌缺乏时间戳或一次性使用机制，攻击者只需具备网络监听能力即可实施攻击，CVSS v2.0 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0443"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.467","remediation":"升级 BMC Patrol 至 3.2 及以上版本，该版本修复了认证会话中缺少随机数（nonce）机制的问题，可有效防止重放攻击。如无法升级，应在网络层面限制 Patrol Agent 管理端口（默认 3181/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并启用 Patrol 的 SSL/TLS 加密通信功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0176","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0605","title":"Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Order Form 1.0 在线购物车 CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过直接访问该 CGI 脚本的特定配置文件或未授权的 URL 路径，获取购物车系统中存储的客户订单信息、交易记录等私密数据。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击条件简单，无需认证即可利用，影响使用该购物车程序的 Web 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0605"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.337","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器上移除或禁用 `order_form.cgi` 脚本。修改 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置文件，限制对 CGI 目录的访问权限，添加 IP 白名单或 HTTP 认证。如仍需购物车功能，应升级至支持安全配置的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce 等），并确保 CGI 脚本不以全局可读权限运行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0605","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0605.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2021/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0180","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0608","title":"PDG Shopping Cart 信息泄露漏洞","description":"PDG Shopping Cart 的 CGI 程序 shopper.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用错误的访问控制配置直接访问未授权的敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用了 PDG Shopping Cart 的早期 Web 服务器，攻击者无需身份认证即可窃取用户订单数据、购物车内容等隐私信息。厂商未提供官方修复补丁，建议升级至更安全的购物车系统或移除不必要的 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0608"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.690","remediation":"立即移除或替换已停止维护的 PDG Shopping Cart，升级至现代受支持的购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）。若无法立即替换，在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置中对 shopper.cgi 添加 IP 白名单访问控制，并移除 CGI 目录的目录浏览权限，防止未授权访问泄露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","http://www.pdgsoft.com/Security/security.html.","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3857","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0608","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0608.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0180.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0182","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0609","title":"SoftCart SoftCart.exe CGI 配置不当信息泄露漏洞","description":"SoftCart 电子商务软件的 CGI 程序 SoftCart.exe 存在错误配置漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求利用该配置缺陷，获取服务器上的敏感信息（如订单数据、客户信息等）。该漏洞影响使用 SoftCart CGI 程序的 Web 服务器，CVE 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级软件版本或限制 CGI 脚本访问权限进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0609"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.817","remediation":"将 SoftCart 订单数据存储目录移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /var/softcart/data），通过 Apache 的 <Directory> 指令或 .htaccess 的 Deny from all 禁止直接访问该目录；将文件权限设置为 600，仅允许 Web 进程用户读取。由于 SoftCart 已停止维护，建议迁移至支持敏感数据加密存储的受支持购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0609","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0609.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2055/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c26f55c1-1cb8-453a-ae44-fe71d70ff34b.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Vulnhub/OZ/oz-1-nikto-8080-output.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0183","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0610","title":"Webcart CGI 程序信息泄露漏洞","description":"Webcart CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，攻击者可利用不安全的访问控制直接获取 Webcart 购物车系统中的敏感信息，包括用户订单详情、联系信息等。该漏洞影响使用 Webcart CGI 的早期电子商务网站，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程访问，属于信息泄露类安全缺陷。建议修改 CGI 脚本权限配置并实施访问控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0610"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.933","remediation":"立即检查服务器上是否仍在运行 Webcart CGI 程序，若无需使用则彻底删除或禁用该 CGI 脚本。如业务必须保留，应限制 CGI 目录权限为仅可执行必要文件，配置 Web 服务器（如 Apache）通过 .htaccess 或 location 指令限制可访问 IP 范围，并禁用目录列表与符号链接跟随。同时建议迁移至现代受支持的电商平台，避免使用已停止维护的 CGI 程序暴露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0610","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0610.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webcart.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99fbdaa8-4c6c-4442-9bb2-6a51e40a9543.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0183.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0721","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0721.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0921","title":"BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 UDP Flooding 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 存在 UDP 泛洪拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 UDP 端口发送大量恶意数据包，导致服务资源耗尽而无法正常响应合法请求。该漏洞影响 BMC Patrol Agent 3.2.5 版本，攻击条件简单，仅需构造持续 UDP 流量即可触发拒绝服务状态。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0921"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.013","remediation":"建议升级 BMC Patrol Agent 至 3.3.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 UDP 端口处理漏洞。如无法升级，可在防火墙配置规则限制对 Patrol Agent UDP 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并启用流量速率限制以缓解 UDP 泛洪攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/4291.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1879"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0721.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0177","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0177.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0606","title":"EZMall 2000 购物车系统 mall2000.cgi 配置不当信息泄露漏洞","description":"EZMall 2000 购物车系统的 CGI 程序 mall2000.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送特制 HTTP 请求利用该程序的错误配置，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 EZMall 2000 购物车系统，CWE-200 信息暴露类别，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，获取系统敏感信息，建议升级至安全版本或修复配置。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0606"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01","updated":"2026-07-14","remediation":"立即修改 mall2000.cgi 的文件权限为 750 或更低，禁止非授权用户直接访问。将该 CGI 脚本移出 Web 可访问目录或添加 HTTP 认证。该产品已停止维护，建议彻底移除 EZMall 2000 组件，迁移至受支持的购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0606.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0606"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0177.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0177.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0177.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0434","title":"XFree86 xfs 符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"XFree86 的 xfs（X 字体服务器）命令存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 xfs 以提升的权限向受限目录写入文件，从而导致权限提升或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 XFree86 的 NetBSD 及其他类 Unix 系统，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0434"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.283","remediation":"升级 XFree86 至 3.3.5 及以上版本以修复 xfs 符号链接漏洞，或应用 NetBSD 厂商发布的对应安全补丁。临时缓解措施：限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，确保 xfs 临时目录（如 /tmp/.X11-unix）具有正确权限（1777）且不可被符号链接攻击利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/359","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0434","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0434.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2g65-vp99-qwv8/GHSA-2g65-vp99-qwv8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/359/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0434.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f067e6f3-94b3-4865-b51d-3ed58fe18b33.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1086","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1086.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1370","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 安装向导信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的安装向导程序 ie5setup.exe 在无人值守安装过程中会禁用系统屏幕保护程序，若安装过程出现故障或中断，拥有物理访问权限的本地用户可趁系统无人看管时直接操作目标主机；同时该程序会禁用任务计划程序服务，导致系统无法按时执行安全关键程序（如自动更新、病毒扫描等），降低系统整体安全性。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1370"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.730","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在运行 ie5setup.exe 完成安装后，手动重新启用屏幕保护程序（控制面板→显示→屏幕保护程序）和任务计划程序服务（services.msc→Task Scheduler→启动类型设为自动并启动服务）。建议改用现代浏览器替代 IE。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92220197414799&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1086.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1906","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1906.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1397","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Index Server 远程注册表管理漏洞","description":"Microsoft Index Server 2.0 在 IIS 4.0 上存在信息泄露漏洞。Index Server 将索引目录的物理路径信息存储在注册表 ContentIndex\\Catalogs 子键下的 AllowedPaths 键值中，由于该注册表项的权限配置不当，本地及远程攻击者可通过访问注册表获取被索引目录的物理路径。攻击者利用此信息可进一步探测目标系统目录结构，为后续攻击提供情报支持。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 IIS 4.0 环境，CVSS v2.0 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1397"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-23","updated":"1999-03-23","remediation":"立即升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）及对应 IIS 版本，Index Server 2.0 和 IIS 4.0 均已停止支持，无法通过补丁修复。如无法升级，可手动收紧注册表键 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\ContentIndex\\Catalogs\\AllowedPaths` 的权限，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的读取权限，并限制对该注册表路径的远程访问。同时建议禁用 Index Server 服务（cisvc）以彻底消除暴露面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1397","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1397.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vvqj-w228-7466/GHSA-vvqj-w228-7466.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1397.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000583.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8c819e08-07e7-43f1-8c2b-fa277db729fe.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1906.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0085","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0428","title":"OpenSSL SSL 会话重用与访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"OpenSSL 和 SSLeay 库存在会话重用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用已建立的 SSL 会话绕过访问控制机制，获取未授权访问权限。该漏洞源于 SSL/TLS 会话管理实现缺陷，攻击者在同一 SSL 会话中未经重新认证即可冒充合法用户，导致会话固定与身份欺骗攻击。影响早期版本的 OpenSSL 和 SSLeay 库，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。通过禁用 SSL 会话重用或更新至修复版本可缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0428"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.500","remediation":"升级 OpenSSL 至 0.9.2b 及以上版本，该版本已修复 SSL 会话重用绕过访问控制的缺陷。当前所有维护中的 OpenSSL 版本（1.x、3.x 系列）均不受此问题影响。若仍使用已停止维护的 SSLeay 库，应迁移至 OpenSSL 最新稳定版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3936","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0428.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0428.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0428","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0428.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/openssl/gb_openssl_CVE-1999-0428.nasl","https://github.com/secure-software-engineering/achilles-benchmark-depscanners/blob/78b391f47cbe64adf7a2e2182ff94be604eb94dd/detection/CVE-1999-0428__org.jruby_openssl_0.9.4.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0428.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0428.yaml","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/openssl/openssl.md","https://github.com/eclipse-ee4j/krazo/blob/a92003e894f263caa501df02fe1812b62ebbb8ee/dependency-check-suppressions.xml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0154","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0154.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0481","title":"OpenBSD poll 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 的 poll 系统调用存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制请求触发 poll 函数异常处理，导致系统内核崩溃或服务不可用。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。建议升级到 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0481"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-22","updated":"1999-03-22","remediation":"立即升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 OpenBSD 2.4 errata 003 号补丁中修复。如无法升级，可下载并应用 OpenBSD 官方提供的 poll(2) 源码补丁（https://www.openbsd.org/errata24.html#poll），重新编译内核后重启系统。对于已停止维护的旧版本，建议迁移至受支持的 OpenBSD 最新稳定版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0154.toml"}]